org.openjdk.tools.javac.comp

类 Annotate

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openjdk.tools.javac.comp.Annotate

  • public class Annotate
extends Object
    Enter annotations onto symbols and types (and trees). This is also a pseudo stage in the compiler taking care of scheduling when annotations are entered.

    This is NOT part of any supported API. If you write code that depends on this, you do so at your own risk. This code and its internal interfaces are subject to change or deletion without notice.
